Adorable wombat Chloe the joey was orphaned after her mother was killed by a car in December . 
  She now lives at Taronga Zoo in Sydney and has found a new friend in a couple of echidnas . 
  She has been inseparable since she came to the zoo three months ago . 
  Chloe recently moved into her new digs alongside her new friends . 
  She is seen trying to take a nap in the mud at the zoo . 
 